de.dfki.embots.behaviorbuilder.model
Class PoseSequenceModel

java.lang.Object
  de.dfki.embots.behaviorbuilder.model.PoseSequenceModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
BBConstants
public class PoseSequenceModel
extends java.lang.Object
implements BBConstants

Wrapper class with similar functionality as EMBRPoseSequence. Keeps sequence of poses that are only assembled to a pose sequence when needed for animation. NOTE: Poses are NOT kept in temporal sorted order. Instead, they are re-indexed. The output is sorted by producing an EMBRPoseSequence which does the sorting automatically (using TreeSet).
